data.description: Completely updated home in 2019,Including Windows, Boiler, completely rewired, New Kitchen with Granite counter tops, refinished Hard Wood Flrs, Updated Bathroom, with large rooms, stain glass windows, original wood work, Carnegie Music Hall library across from John F Kennedy Park. Exterior- TREX Deck (22x14) added in 2021, home has a 2 car garage, and off street parking pad, along with a fenced in yard. Minutes from the Waterfront, Squirrel Hill, Oakland, and Downtown Pittsburgh.
